  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Cosplay costumes, fast fashion and bold, exotic styles. Given the state of world trade, was definitely not produced anywhere in Asia. Does that make it less authentic? You be the judge. Having a couple of these in the closet is essential for any performer, no matter their stripe.</p><ul><li><p>Can be sourced by any fixer or found at any Night Market.</p></li><li><p>Once a week while being worn, the user gains <strong>+2 to Acting, Play Instrument, Wardrobe &amp; Style, Dance, and Conversation</strong> checks for 12 hours.</p></li><li><p>Characters can only benefit from one outfit's provided bonuses at a time.</p></li></ul>"
